message.body: Hey beautiful. Are we still on for tomorrow afternoon?
absolutely! do you have a time in mind?
sure! did you have plans for us, or...
A walk perhaps and then dinner later so you could wear your dress.
so i should maybe just bring it along and change? sorry to pester you with questions, i'm just trying to mentally map out the evening. :)
i don't even have to wear the dress. we could totally save it for a more worthy occasion.
Ok save the dress for now. I still have to get ready so let's say half part four, ok?
